title: Front Line Assembly - AirMech (2012) [FLAC]
description:
AirMech is a studio album by Vancouver industrial band Front Line Assembly. The album was released by Carbon Games in 2012 as the soundtrack for free-to-play real-time strategy game AirMech.

Tracklisting:

01. AirMech
02. Arise
03. Pulse Charge
04. Prep for Combat
05. System Anomaly
06. Mech Killer
07. Everything That Was Before
08. Lose
09. Burning Skyline
10. Stealth Mech
11. Death Level
12. Prime Empiricism
